SUMMARY:Eric Spinney [@exs]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-02-24 Tue 14:30-16:00>\n• Started DLS with Chanu\, try st
 arch in water as a start.\n• Nanodrop was tempermental last time but Eric 
 didn't inform\, so 40%\n  and 50% DES repeat was "wasted".  HB should chec
 k 5th floor\n  instrument.\n• Discussed internal reference\, possibly 0.18
 wt% glucose (50%\n  conversion).
CATEGORIES:@exs,BRG
END:VEVENT
