 d glycerol water\, this time capturing\n  photo and/or video.\n• ☐ based o
 n best mixing method\, repeat with polyelectrolytes (with\n  salt).\n• ☐ G
 iovanni should read about NMR and PECs before contacting Weiguo.
CATEGORIES:@gxg,BRG
END:VEVENT
